body.name: ASUS TUF Gaming GT502 ATX Mid-Tower Computer Case with ASUS TUF Gaming TF120 ARGB Chassis Fan 3 Pack
deliveryMessages: Delivery Friday, February 16. Order within 3 hrs 17 mins
features: Dual-Chamber Design divides the GT502 case internals into two chambers allowing you to build and configure independent cooling zones for the CPU and GPU.
The TF120 fans provide class-leading airflow and low noise levels with advanced fluid dynamic bearing provides up to 250,000 hours of operation.
The GT502 case offers versatile graphic card mounting options - stand graphics card up vertically with included mount or slot it directly into motherboard to banish sag.
The TF120 fans have anti-vibration pads to reduce noise by damping rattling and vibration.
The GT502 case comes with tempered glass panels at front and side providing a tinted view of main chamber.
body.description: ASUS TUF Gaming GT502 ATX Mid-Tower Computer Case with Front Panel RGB Button, USB 3.2 Type-C and 2X USB 3.0 PortsBuild your battle station with the TUF Gaming GT502 Gaming Case featuring front panel USB 3.2 Type-C and 2x USB 3.0 Ports, support for 2- way Graphic Card Mounting Orientation, and 360mm and 280mm Radiators. The TUF Gaming GT502 puts your prized hardware up front and holds your six with a stack of cooling options to slay thermals and express ultimate performance.
